# React Login Form

This repository contains a **React Login Form** built using React.js. The form is styled with modern design principles and includes basic input validation for username and password fields.

## Features

- Responsive design for all screen sizes
- Input validation for username and password fields
- Reusable and modular components
- Clean and well-documented code

## Demo

![React Login Form Demo](./assets/demo-image.png)  
_A screenshot of the React Login Form_

## Technologies Used

- **React.js**: For building the UI components
- **CSS/SCSS**: For styling the form
- **Formik/Yup** *(Optional)*: For form handling and validation
- **Axios/Firebase** *(Optional)*: For backend API integration (if applicable)

